SNF_REVIEW_QUESTIONS: Which cloud platforms are supported by Snowflake? (Select all that apply.)
SNF_ANSWER_DESCRIPTIONS: Snowflake is supported on AWS, Google Cloud, and Microsoft Azure.

SNF_REVIEW_QUESTIONS: What feature allows users to recover deleted data in Snowflake?
SNF_ANSWER_DESCRIPTIONS: Time Travel allows users to access historical data that has been deleted or modified within a specified retention period.

SNF_REVIEW_QUESTIONS: What is the minimum Snowflake edition required to enable multi-cluster virtual warehouses?
SNF_ANSWER_DESCRIPTIONS: Multi-cluster virtual warehouses are supported starting from the Enterprise edition.

SNF_REVIEW_QUESTIONS: True or False: Snowflake automatically manages the scaling of virtual warehouses to match the workload.
SNF_ANSWER_DESCRIPTIONS: Virtual warehouses can be scaled up or down automatically based on the current query workload in Snowflake.

SNF_REVIEW_QUESTIONS: Which of the following features are included in Snowflakeâ€™s Business Critical edition? (Select all that apply.)
SNF_ANSWER_DESCRIPTIONS: The Business Critical edition includes advanced security features such as Tri-Secret Secure, dynamic data masking, and Virtual Private Snowflake.
